(340, 7, '2018-12-13 22:02:47', '2018-12-13 15:02:47', '<h4><span id=\"1_Ep_kieu_la_gi\"><strong>1. Ép kiểu là gì</strong></span></h4>\r\nÉp kiểu là cách để chuyển đổi một biến từ kiểu dữ liệu này sang kiểu dữ liệu khác. Ví dụ như int sang float, float sang int,…\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Cách sử dụng</strong>\r\n\r\nGiả sử ta có ví dụ sau:\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-plain-wrap\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-main\">\r\n<table class=\"crayon-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"crayon-row\">\r\n<td class=\"crayon-nums \" data-settings=\"show\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-nums-content\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-1\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-2\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-3\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-4\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-5\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-6\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-7\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-8\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-9\">9</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"crayon-code\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-pre\">\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-1\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-p\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-2\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-p\">#include&lt;string.h&gt;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-3\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">int</span> <span class=\"crayon-e\">main</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">{</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-4\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">    int</span> <span class=\"crayon-v\">a</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">10</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-5\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">    float</span> <span class=\"crayon-v\">b</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">20.5</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-6\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-v\">    a</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-v\">b</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-7\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-e\">    printf</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-s\">\"%d\"</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">,</span><span class=\"crayon-v\">a</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-8\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-st\">  return</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">0</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868ed139550841-9\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-sy\">}</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nỞ đây a là kiểu số nguyên còn b là kiểu số thực nhưng ta cố tình gán b cho a. Kết quả:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1631 aligncenter td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 973px) 100vw, 973px\" srcset=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56.png 973w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56-300x158.png 300w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56-768x405.png 768w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56-696x367.png 696w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/56-797x420.png 797w\" alt=\"\" width=\"973\" height=\"513\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTa được kết quả là 20 là do khoảng số thực của ta bao giờ cũng lớn hơn số nguyên nên đã gây ra sự mất mát dữ liệu.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Chú ý:</strong> Trong lập trình không nên ép kiểu lớn hơn về kiểu nhỏ hơn tránh gây mất mát dữ liệu.</em>\r\n\r\nĐể ép kiểu nhỏ hơn sang lớn hơn, ta sử dụng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cú pháp</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868f7153758667\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-plain-wrap\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-main\">\r\n<table class=\"crayon-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"crayon-row\">\r\n<td class=\"crayon-nums \" data-settings=\"show\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-nums-content\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868f7153758667-1\">1</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"crayon-code\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-pre\">\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868f7153758667-1\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-v\">dulieu</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-e\">ten </span><span class=\"crayon-v\">kieu</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-v\">dulieugan</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cách sử dụng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTa có ví dụ ép kiểu từ int sang float. Cụ thể:\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-plain-wrap\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-main\">\r\n<table class=\"crayon-table\" style=\"height: 254px;\" width=\"759\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"crayon-row\">\r\n<td class=\"crayon-nums \" data-settings=\"show\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-nums-content\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-1\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-2\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-3\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-4\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-5\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-6\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-7\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-8\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-9\">9</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"crayon-code\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-pre\">\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-1\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-p\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-2\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-p\">#include&lt;string.h&gt;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-3\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">int</span> <span class=\"crayon-e\">main</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">{</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-4\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">    int</span> <span class=\"crayon-v\">a</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">40</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-5\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-t\">    float</span> <span class=\"crayon-v\">b</span> <span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">20.5</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-6\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-v\">    b</span><span class=\"crayon-o\">=</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-t\">float</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-v\">a</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-7\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-e\">    printf</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">(</span><span class=\"crayon-s\">\"%f\"</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">,</span><span class=\"crayon-v\">b</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">)</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-8\" class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\"><span class=\"crayon-st\">  return</span> <span class=\"crayon-cn\">0</span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;</span></div>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5ab32867868fb233390629-9\" class=\"crayon-line\"><span class=\"crayon-sy\">}</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nKết quả:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1632 aligncenter td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 977px) 100vw, 977px\" srcset=\"http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57.png 977w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57-300x157.png 300w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57-768x402.png 768w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57-696x365.png 696w, http://laptrinhc.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/57-801x420.png 801w\" alt=\"\" width=\"977\" height=\"512\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTa có thể thấy dữ liệu không hề bị mất.', 'Lập trình C: Bài 15 - Ép kiểu', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '339-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-13 22:02:47', '2018-12-13 15:02:47', '', 339, 'http://80.211.52.162/web-teach-code/blog/2018/12/13/339-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
